              <div class="text-4xl mb-3">&check;</div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2" style={`color: ${colors.midnight};`}>Application Received!</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">We&rsquo;ll review your profile and get back to you within 24 hours with your personalized funding roadmap.</p>
              <a
